#. module: non_profit_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:non_profit_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"View team availability by toggling on their calendars to avoid conflicts."
msgstr ""
"ເບິ່ງຄວາມພ້ອມຂອງທີມໂດຍການເປີດປະຕິທິນຂອງເຂົາເຈົ້າເພື່ອຫຼີກລ່ຽງການນັດໝາຍທີ່ຊ້ຳຊ້ອນ."

#. module: non_profit_organization
#: model:planning.role,name:non_profit_organization.planning_role_1
