#. module: non_profit_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:non_profit_organization.website_footer_qweb_view
msgid ""
"We are a team of passionate people whose\n"
"                                            goal is to improve everyone's life.<br/>Our services\n"
"                                            are designed for small to medium size companies."
msgstr ""
"ພວກເຮົາແມ່ນທີມງານທີ່ມີຄວາມມຸ່ງໝັ້ນ\n"
"                                            ເພື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້ຊີວິດຂອງທຸກຄົນດີຂຶ້ນ.<br/>ການບໍລິກ"
"ານຂອງພວກເຮົາ\n"
"                                            ຖືກອອກແບບມາສຳລັບບໍລິສັດຂະໜາດນ້ອຍຫາຂະໜາດ"
"ກາງ."

#. module: non_profit_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:non_profit_organization.website_homepage_qweb_view
msgid ""
"We don’t come in with all the answers. We\n"
"                                                        listen, build together, and adjust when\n"
"                                                        things change.&amp;nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"ພວກເຮົາບໍ່ໄດ້ມີຄຳຕອບໃຫ້ທຸກຢ່າງ. ພວກເຮົາ\n"
"                                                        ຮັບຟັງ, ຮ່ວມກັນສ້າງ, ແລະ ປັ"
"ບປຸງເມື່ອ\n"
"                                                        ສິ່ງຕ່າງໆປ່ຽນແປ"
"ງ.&amp;nbsp;"

#. module: non_profit_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:non_profit_organization.website_homepage_qweb_view
msgid ""
"We focus on creating impactful programs,\n"
"                                                        ensuring sustainable changes&amp;nbsp;that\n"
"                                                        meet community needs."
msgstr ""
"ພວກເຮົາເນັ້ນໃສ່ການສ້າງໂຄງການທີ່ມີຜົນກະທົບ,\n"
"                                                        ເພື່ອໃຫ້ເກີດການປ່ຽນແປງທີ່ຍືນຍົ"
"ງ\n"
"                                                        ທີ່ຕອບສະໜອງຄວາມຕ້ອງການຂອ"
"ງຊຸມຊົນ."

#. module: non_profit_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:non_profit_organization.website_homepage_qweb_view
msgid ""
"We say what we do, and we do what we say.\n"
"                                                        People deserve honesty, not promises we\n"
"                                                        can’t keep.&amp;nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"ພວກເຮົາເວົ້າໃນສິ່ງທີ່ເຮັດ, ແລະ ເຮັດໃນສິ່ງທີ່ເວົ້າ.\n"
"                                                        ທຸກຄົນຄວນໄດ້ຮັບຄວາມຈິງໃຈ, "
"ບໍ່ແມ່ນຄຳສັນຍາ\n"
"                                                        ທີ່ພວກເຮົາເຮັດບໍ່ໄ"
"ດ້.&amp;nbsp;"

#. module: non_profit_organization
#: model_terms:survey.survey,description:non_profit_organization.survey_survey_1
msgid ""
"We truly appreciate your presence and support. To help us improve future "
"events and better serve our community, we kindly ask you to take 2–3 minutes"
" to complete this short survey."
msgstr ""
"ພວກເຮົາຂໍຂອບໃຈຢ່າງຈິງໃຈສຳລັບການເຂົ້າຮ່ວມ ແລະ ການສະໜັບສະໜູນຂອງທ່ານ. ເພື່ອຊ່ວຍພວກເຮົາປັບປຸງງານໃນ"
"ອະນາຄົດໃຫ້ດີຂຶ້ນ, ຂໍຄວາມກະລຸນາໃຊ້ເວລາ 2-3 ນາທີເພື່ອຕອບແບບສອບຖາມສັ້ນໆນີ້."

#. module: non_profit_organization
#: model_terms:product.public.category,website_description:non_profit_organization.product_public_category_1
msgid "Wear your support proudly with our stylish, mission-driven clothing."
msgstr ""
"ສະແດງການສະໜັບສະໜູນຂອງທ່ານດ້ວຍຄວາມພາກພູມໃຈ ຜ່ານເຄື່ອງນຸ່ງທີ່ມີສະໄຕລ໌ ແລະ ມີຄວາມໝາຍ."

#. module: non_profit_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:non_profit_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Website &amp; eCommerce promotes your NGO online by sharing your mission and actions,\n"
"            selling memberships, merchandise, collecting donations, and managing petitions forms for\n"
"            signatures."
msgstr ""
"ເວັບໄຊ &amp; ອີຄອມເມີຊ ຊ່ວຍໂປຣໂມດອົງການຂອງທ່ານທາງອອນລາຍໂດຍການແບ່ງປັນພາລະກິດ ແລະ ກິດຈະກ"
"ຳ,\n"
"            ຂາຍສະມາຊິກພາບ, ສິນຄ້າ, ຮັບການບໍລິຈາກ, ແລະ ຈັດການຟອມລົງລາຍຊື່."

