"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries &gt;\n"
"                    Upgrade your Non-profit organization package and check the related box."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານບໍ່ໄດ້ນຳເຂົ້າຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງບໍ? ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້. ໄປທີ່ ແອັບ &gt; ກຸ່ມທຸລະກິດ &gt;\n"
"                    ອັບເກຣດແພັກເກັດອົງການບໍ່ຫວັງຜົນກຳໄລ ແລະ ໝາຍເອົາຫ້ອງທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ."

#. module: non_profit_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:non_profit_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of various flows\n"
"            you can quickly execute with this package using Odoo."
